article.linkText: Choh scores 20 to carry Brown over Columbia 93-74
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Tamenang Choh scored 20 points and Brown topped Columbia 93-74 on Saturday. Paxson Wojcik had 15 points for Brown (10-11, 2-4 Ivy League). Nana Owusu-Anane added 12 points. Perry Cowan had 11 points. Ike Nweke had 16 points and nine rebounds for the Lions (4-12, 1-3). Zavian McLean added 11 points. Cameron Shockley-Okeke had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
